quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  26,112,"Naboola mbu: “Emanyiile shina kalia akabakholanga?"
  26,113,"Ne okhubalilwa ebikhole khwabu khuli butswa khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, abayie mumanyangakhwo."
  26,114,"Ne esie shinditsa okhulonda Abasuubili batsie ehale tawe."
  26,115,"Esie shendi shiosishiosi tawe halali omwikanyilisi owa habulafu.”"
  26,116,"Nibaboola mbu: “Nolalekhana ninaafu tawe ewe Nuhu, toto olaba mubalia balalaswa amachina.”"
  26,117,"Nuhu naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto Abandu banje bayingasiye."
  26,118,"Kho, khalaka eshina hakari wanje ninabo okhukhalaka okhulayi, ne uhabine esie nende balia bali halala ninasi mubasuubili.”"
  26,119,"Kho mana nikhumuhabina ye nende balia bali halala ninaye musafina yitsule."
  26,120,"Mana okhurula awo, nikhusishia balia abatong’a."
  26,121,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko, halali abaanji mubo shibali bokhusuubila tawe."
  26,122,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,123,"Babu A’di boosi bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,124,"(Betsulisie) Olwa Omusiani wabu, Hud yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimularia Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,125,"Toto esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa omwisikwa."
  26,126,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,127,"Ne shebasabanga khu kano omurungo kwosikwosi tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,128,"Koo, mumbakhanga buli khwitulo, eshitsulisio shiokhukhola kalia kabulamwo oluchendo."
  26,129,"Ne mumbakhanga tsingoba mpara mbu mulimenya tsinyanga tsioosi?"
  26,130,"Ne nimusera, museranga nobufuru."
  26,131,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile."
  26,132,"Ne rie ulia owabahelesia kalia akamumanyile."
  26,133,"Yabahelesia emiruko nende Abana abasiani."
  26,134,"Nende emikunda nende tsisebele."
  26,135,"Toto ebaririranga eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo.”"
  26,136,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ni nashilala butswa khwifwe, nokhuchelela nohomba noobula okhukhuchelela."